    "title": "推荐一个开源项目：mp-publisher-将obsidian文章复制到微信公众号",
    "content": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><section class=\"mp-content-section\" style=\"\"><blockquote dir=\"auto\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 10px; background: #f6f8fa; margin: 0.8em 0; color: #6a737d; font-style: italic; word-wrap: break-word;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\">\n<p>今天逛<strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4a4a4a;\">少数派</strong>的时候发现一个很好用的插件：<strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4a4a4a;\">mp-publisher</strong>，吸引我的有两点：</p>\n<ol style=\"padding-left: 32px; color: #4a4a4a;\">\n<li dir=\"auto\" style=\" font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\"><section>支持自定义风格配置（字体，主题等）</section></li>\n<li dir=\"auto\" style=\" font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\"><section>可视化界面，配置简单</section></li>\n<li dir=\"auto\" style=\" font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\"><section>支持查看运行日志，实时查看报错信息</section></li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\" style=\"line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1em; font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\">作者原文：<a data-tooltip-position=\"top\" aria-label=\"https://sspai.com/post/106120\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://sspai.com/post/106120\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #e0e0e0; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">我写了个插件，一键从 Obsidian 发布到公众号后台 - 少数派</a><br />\n链接：<a data-tooltip-position=\"top\" aria-label=\"https://github.com/joeytoday/obsidian-mp-publisher\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/joeytoday/obsidian-mp-publisher\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #e0e0e0; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">GitHub - joeytoday/obsidian-mp-publisher: 自定义主题预览，并发布到公众号草稿箱。</a><br />\n快速开始：<a data-tooltip-position=\"top\" aria-label=\"https://github.com/joeytoday/obsidian-mp-publisher/blob/main/QUICKSTART.md\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/joeytoday/obsidian-mp-publisher/blob/main/QUICKSTART.md\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #e0e0e0; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">obsidian-mp-publisher/QUICKSTART.md at main · joeytoday/obsidian-mp-publisher · GitHub</a></p>\n<h1 data-heading=\"补充：如何打开 obsidian 控制台？\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 32px 0 0; font-size: 2em; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.5;; font-family: -apple-system;\"><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;\">补充：如何打开 obsidian 控制台？</span><span class=\"after\" style=\"\"></span></h1>\n<blockquote dir=\"auto\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 10px; background: #f6f8fa; margin: 0.8em 0; color: #6a737d; font-style: italic; word-wrap: break-word;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\">\n<p>回家之后尝试使用此插件，发现无法获取到<strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4a4a4a;\">素材库图片</strong>，想查看运行信息</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\" style=\"line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1em; font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\">Obsidian 打开控制台：</p>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 32px; color: #4a4a4a;\">\n<li dir=\"auto\" style=\" font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\"><section><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4a4a4a;\">Windows</strong>：<code style=\"background: #f8f8f8; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #333; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid #eee;\">CTRL + SHIFT + i</code></section></li>\n<li dir=\"auto\" style=\" font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\"><section><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4a4a4a;\">MacOS</strong>：<code style=\"background: #f8f8f8; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #333; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid #eee;\">CMD + OPTION + i</code></section></li>\n<li dir=\"auto\" style=\" font-size: 1em; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 16px;\"><section><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #4a4a4a;\">Linux</strong>：<code style=\"background: #f8f8f8; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #333; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid #eee;\">CTRL + SHIFT + i</code><br />\n<img src=\"app://a9dc45ebdc25a007643f2432eabdc8b7eb4e/C:/Users/%E7%BB%BF%E5%AD%97/Desktop/lsq_learn/img/Pasted%20image%2020260224225704.png?1771945024068\" alt=\"Pasted image 20260224225704.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 1em auto; display: block;\" /> 发现是 IP 错误，在微信开发平台配置 IP白名单后即可解决</section></li>\n</ul></section></div></div>",
    "updateTime": 1772028013874
  }
}